yTime":"2018-11-15T01:01:30.000Z","msg":"林夕拿着Juno新歌詞《弱水三千》，邊看邊說：「不應該這樣寫！」不滿這句又不滿那句，原來作品越看越不滿，創作人才會有進步，自吹自擂已經過時。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記：Juno新歌也有佛語？如：「山水非山水，凍了變雪堆。山水本山水，遇熱若霧水。」四句？<br />\n<br />\n林：哈哈哈！現在回看，不應該寫得如此抽象了！<br />\n<br />\n記：每次看回作品也不滿？<br />\n<br />\n林：當然，每次看總有缺點，若永遠覺得作品出色，作者已出現問題，因為已沒有創作力，正在退步。創作是越看越不滿，只覺前作出色，下一個作品，一定遜色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/retails/daily/article/20090810/13080014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fretails%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090810%2F13080014&d=YnhgAe5tbPrEvEKdRa5CsgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c5a0438d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fretails%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090810%2F13080014&h=ea87ecdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/retails/daily/article/20090810/13080014</a><br />\n<br />\n訪問條片好似揾唔翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0b77b2eb3121b83deb99a287d1ca0a009d0942","tid":900533,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:09:19.000Z","msg":"約定"},{"pid":"7b9cf34f512f10f1e54c64d5dbc5c35bc36e4ff9","tid":900533,"uid":118830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:14:01.000Z","msg":"其實首歌講咩"},{"pid":"2d598c9104f754acbfe64b44c265bae46b744f9d","tid":900533,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:26:55.000Z","msg":"相戀很難<br />\n不來也不去<br />\n失憶蝴蝶"},{"pid":"67fcecb8d5b18ff2f31f980cbd20d633ddfa5a13","tid":900533,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:29:43.000Z","msg":"櫻吹雪 又如何？"},{"pid":"0eeb21378075566acaa49c28af368c4b39af8b06","tid":900533,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b9cf34f512f10f1e54c64d5dbc5c35bc36e4ff9","tid":900533,"uid":118830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:14:01.000Z","msg":"其實首歌講咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:30:43.000Z","msg":"循環既水，唔同形態孕育萬物 玩弄萬物"},{"pid":"dc5c4b5eed7bc74c64a06a9b5b9516d6de5b1f87","tid":900533,"uid":201726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:20:51.000Z","msg":"彳亍 又如何"},{"pid":"0332675570d87e883a70dd6f3e98ab622bf08e43","tid":900533,"uid":59996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc5c4b5eed7bc74c64a06a9b5b9516d6de5b1f87","tid":900533,"uid":201726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:20:51.000Z","msg":"彳亍 又如何"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:55:37.000Z","msg":"首曲唔係好鍾意，哂左d 詞"},{"pid":"02e2f889abd763f2c36439ab410c80c3c50c5341","tid":900533,"uid":111571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:56:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3db245f6cb2b685d3dbddb04cf974189bed9a2dc","tid":900533,"uid":36818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:59:25.000Z","msg":"俗世的愛侶誰可永相戀<br />\n談情遊戲我早厭倦<br />\n若果這剎那時空<br />\n隨著我的書本扭轉<br />\n那痛快故事必定賞素願<br />\n<br />\n* 小玉典珠釵 鉛華求長埋<br />\n祝君把新歡 乘龍投豪門<br />\n我要是變心 有誰為我盡情罵<br />\n小玉休相迫 檀郎無忘情<br />\n三載失釵風 瑤台求重逢<br />\n我叫天搶地誰過問<br />\n實際景況已無可再更改<br />\n雷同情節永不似期待 自古書<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n說梁祝 寧願化蝶飛出苦痛<br />\n我也要化碟躲入傳說內<br />\n<br />\n# 庵中孤清清 長平難逃情<br />\n江山悲災損 流離仍重圓<br />\n我偶然與她見面 亦覺甚疲倦<br />\n花燭映規 難為郎情長<br />\n交杯飲砒霜 泉台諧盟約<br />\n我散心解悶誰作伴<br />\n<br />\n@ 重合劍釵修補破鏡<br />\n只有寄情戲曲與文字 盟誓永守<br />\n地老天荒以身盼待<br />\n早已變成絕世傳奇事"}]}